			<div class="comment-content"><p>I know, when I heard that I was so sad because I felt like, I would&#8217;ve come to his house to help if I could. But after hearing that he had Parkinson&#8217;s I felt that maybe he felt he had done enough and he wanted to go on his terms. Whatever reason, he is greatly missed and I will be blessed knowing that my children will pass his talent on to their kids and in that way he will never die.</p>
</div>

